query:
INSERT INTO prices (symbol, ts, open, low, high, close, volume, duration)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
            ON CONFLICT (symbol, ts) DO UPDATE SET
                open=$3,
                low=$4,
                high=$5,
                close=$6,
                volume=$7,
                duration=$8
